HEADWORD: Oxaluric
<hw>Ox`a*lur"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Oxal</ets>yl
+ <ets>urea</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or
